{
  "locale": "zh-CN",
  "duration": 449.133333,
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiaNeural",
  "rate": "+50%",
  "source": "final edge-tts audio and VTT; utterances placed from measured audible bounds",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "c01-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "你知道怎么给 AI 智能体高信号上下文吗？",
      "gapBefore": 0,
      "audioDuration": 3.072,
      "audioStart": 0,
      "spokenStart": 0.155,
      "spokenEnd": 2.476,
      "actualGapBefore": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "接下来我来告诉你，Anthropic 是怎么解决这个问题的。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.504,
      "audioStart": 2.49,
      "spokenStart": 2.636,
      "spokenEnd": 5.406,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "视频全程干货高价值，让你成为更擅长使用 AI 的人，内容较长，点点关注收藏不迷路。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.928,
      "audioStart": 5.359,
      "spokenStart": 5.506,
      "spokenEnd": 10.729,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "Anthropic 把上下文看成有限的注意力预算。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.928,
      "audioStart": 10.732,
      "spokenStart": 10.889,
      "spokenEnd": 13.067,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "窗口越满，下一步真正重要的信号越容易变弱，判断也会偏离当前目标。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.112,
      "audioStart": 13.023,
      "spokenStart": 13.167,
      "spokenEnd": 17.561,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "提示词越长，AI 智能体越可能追着旧细节跑。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.408,
      "audioStart": 17.573,
      "spokenStart": 17.721,
      "spokenEnd": 20.396,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "解决办法，是六部分高信号包：目标、规则、工具、示例、检索和状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.424,
      "audioStart": 20.355,
      "spokenStart": 20.496,
      "spokenEnd": 25.21,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "看注意力预算。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.416,
      "audioStart": 25.226,
      "spokenStart": 25.37,
      "spokenEnd": 26.073,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "原始历史塞满窗口时，目标会被挤小。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.976,
      "audioStart": 26.022,
      "spokenStart": 26.173,
      "spokenEnd": 28.42,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "只保留当前约束和有效证据，目标重新变大。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.408,
      "audioStart": 28.37,
      "spokenStart": 28.52,
      "spokenEnd": 31.198,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u04",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "其余信息移到窗口外，需要时再检索。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.904,
      "audioStart": 31.157,
      "spokenStart": 31.298,
      "spokenEnd": 33.467,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "每一步只让 AI 智能体看见四件事：目标、约束、证据和当前状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.16,
      "audioStart": 33.478,
      "spokenStart": 33.627,
      "spokenEnd": 38.071,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "其他信息先留在窗口外，真正需要时再取，判断完成后再更新状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.872,
      "audioStart": 38.027,
      "spokenStart": 38.171,
      "spokenEnd": 42.325,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "核心判断只有一句：给 AI 智能体支持下一步行动的最小充分上下文，并随着长期任务持续更新。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.528,
      "audioStart": 42.338,
      "spokenStart": 42.485,
      "spokenEnd": 48.293,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "上下文包含模型生成下一次回复时能看到的全部 token：系统指令、工具定义、示例、检索到的文档、消息历史、中间结果和当前请求。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 9.504,
      "audioStart": 48.327,
      "spokenStart": 48.473,
      "spokenEnd": 57.262,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "上下文工程管理的是这整个状态，不只是开头那一段提示词。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.104,
      "audioStart": 57.214,
      "spokenStart": 57.362,
      "spokenEnd": 60.741,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "Anthropic 把上下文描述为有限资源，而且新增内容的边际收益会下降。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.728,
      "audioStart": 60.749,
      "spokenStart": 60.901,
      "spokenEnd": 64.901,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "有关 context rot 的研究反复看到一种现象：材料越多，模型越可能难以准确找回藏在其中的相关信息。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.816,
      "audioStart": 64.849,
      "spokenStart": 65.001,
      "spokenEnd": 71.108,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "窗口更大，不代表注意力免费。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.4,
      "audioStart": 71.067,
      "spokenStart": 71.208,
      "spokenEnd": 72.885,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这解释了为什么超长提示词仍会失败。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.048,
      "audioStart": 72.897,
      "spokenStart": 73.045,
      "spokenEnd": 75.376,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "正确规则可能确实写进去了，但周围还有过期计划、重复说明、原始日志和一长串边缘情况。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.696,
      "audioStart": 75.333,
      "spokenStart": 75.476,
      "spokenEnd": 81.448,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "智能体在解决任务前，先要猜哪些内容仍然有效、权威而且与当前步骤有关。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.424,
      "audioStart": 81.397,
      "spokenStart": 81.548,
      "spokenEnd": 86.236,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "所以，好的上下文工程首先是筛选。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.904,
      "audioStart": 86.254,
      "spokenStart": 86.396,
      "spokenEnd": 88.581,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "每个关键步骤开始前，都问一句：什么信息会改变下一步判断？",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.392,
      "audioStart": 88.53,
      "spokenStart": 88.681,
      "spokenEnd": 92.348,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "保留目标、必要约束、当前证据和实时状态；",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.6,
      "audioStart": 92.295,
      "spokenStart": 92.448,
      "spokenEnd": 95.308,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u04",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "能够稍后获取的参考细节，只保留索引。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.096,
      "audioStart": 95.26,
      "spokenStart": 95.408,
      "spokenEnd": 97.778,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "筛选还要持续进行。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.872,
      "audioStart": 97.789,
      "spokenStart": 97.938,
      "spokenEnd": 99.088,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "工具调用带来新证据，错误暴露新边界，完成里程碑后，原始轨迹可以换成紧凑状态摘要。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.192,
      "audioStart": 99.031,
      "spokenStart": 99.188,
      "spokenEnd": 104.654,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "第十步需要的上下文，不会和第一步完全一样。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.312,
      "audioStart": 104.604,
      "spokenStart": 104.754,
      "spokenEnd": 107.325,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最小不等于短。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 107.343,
      "spokenStart": 107.485,
      "spokenEnd": 108.269,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "复杂迁移仍可能需要完整验收条件、仓库约定和风险控制。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.44,
      "audioStart": 108.229,
      "spokenStart": 108.369,
      "spokenEnd": 112.09,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "标准不是字最少，而是足以支持预期行为的最小集合。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.696,
      "audioStart": 112.042,
      "spokenStart": 112.19,
      "spokenEnd": 115.167,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "小结。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.128,
      "audioStart": 115.179,
      "spokenStart": 115.327,
      "spokenEnd": 115.738,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "第一，把上下文当作有限注意力预算，而不是无限存储。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.96,
      "audioStart": 115.69,
      "spokenStart": 115.838,
      "spokenEnd": 119.058,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，更多 token 可能稀释下一步最重要的指令。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.288,
      "audioStart": 119.063,
      "spokenStart": 119.218,
      "spokenEnd": 121.767,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，保留最小充分集合，并随任务变化持续刷新。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.864,
      "audioStart": 121.777,
      "spokenStart": 121.927,
      "spokenEnd": 125.071,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "先把系统指令写在合适的抽象层级。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.88,
      "audioStart": 125.101,
      "spokenStart": 125.251,
      "spokenEnd": 127.404,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "一端是把所有分支硬编码成脆弱的规则；",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.24,
      "audioStart": 127.351,
      "spokenStart": 127.504,
      "spokenEnd": 130.023,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "另一端只是说“把事情做好”，默认智能体知道没有明说的标准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.104,
      "audioStart": 129.978,
      "spokenStart": 130.123,
      "spokenEnd": 133.508,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "更有效的中间位置会明确目标、边界和判断原则，同时给推理留下空间。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.208,
      "audioStart": 133.519,
      "spokenStart": 133.668,
      "spokenEnd": 138.146,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "背景、指令、工具说明和输出要求可以分区组织。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.936,
      "audioStart": 138.102,
      "spokenStart": 138.246,
      "spokenEnd": 141.453,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "格式有帮助，但真正决定效果的是内容是否清楚、优先级是否明确。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.944,
      "audioStart": 141.404,
      "spokenStart": 141.553,
      "spokenEnd": 145.778,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "接着检查工具。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 145.797,
      "spokenStart": 145.938,
      "spokenEnd": 146.722,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "工具不只是一个动作，还是智能体与环境之间的契约。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.6,
      "audioStart": 146.671,
      "spokenStart": 146.822,
      "spokenEnd": 149.698,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "名称、说明、参数、错误处理和返回数据都会进入上下文，并影响智能体选择哪一个动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.456,
      "audioStart": 149.646,
      "spokenStart": 149.798,
      "spokenEnd": 155.53,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "功能重叠会制造模糊决策，也会浪费注意力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.36,
      "audioStart": 155.537,
      "spokenStart": 155.69,
      "spokenEnd": 158.31,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "如果人都说不清两个工具分别什么时候使用，就不能期待智能体稳定判断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.944,
      "audioStart": 158.261,
      "spokenStart": 158.41,
      "spokenEnd": 162.627,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "保留最小可用工具集，让每个工具职责单一、输入明确、结果紧凑。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.728,
      "audioStart": 162.572,
      "spokenStart": 162.727,
      "spokenEnd": 166.722,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "然后筛选示例。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 166.74,
      "spokenStart": 166.882,
      "spokenEnd": 167.69,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "堆满边缘情况看起来很全面，却容易把规律埋掉。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.672,
      "audioStart": 167.643,
      "spokenStart": 167.79,
      "spokenEnd": 170.745,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "Anthropic 更推荐少量、多样、典型的例子，让智能体看见预期模式、必要变化和一条重要边界。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.408,
      "audioStart": 170.693,
      "spokenStart": 170.845,
      "spokenEnd": 176.519,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "高信号不是固定字数。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.016,
      "audioStart": 176.529,
      "spokenStart": 176.679,
      "spokenEnd": 177.975,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它指一段信息有明确工作：确定结果、约束行为、选择工具、展示模式、提供证据或暴露停止条件。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.984,
      "audioStart": 177.928,
      "spokenStart": 178.075,
      "spokenEnd": 184.344,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "只有完全不承担这些工作时，才应该删除。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.12,
      "audioStart": 184.288,
      "spokenStart": 184.444,
      "spokenEnd": 186.829,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "小结。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 186.841,
      "spokenStart": 186.989,
      "spokenEnd": 187.4,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "第一，系统指令要落在硬编码和空泛之间的合适层级。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.864,
      "audioStart": 187.355,
      "spokenStart": 187.5,
      "spokenEnd": 190.647,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，工具要清楚、高效，并尽量减少功能重叠。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.744,
      "audioStart": 190.662,
      "spokenStart": 190.807,
      "spokenEnd": 193.837,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，用少量典型示例教会智能体真正的模式。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.648,
      "audioStart": 193.848,
      "spokenStart": 193.997,
      "spokenEnd": 196.925,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "不少系统会在智能体开始前，把所有可能相关的文档全部塞进上下文。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 4.824,
      "audioStart": 196.955,
      "spokenStart": 197.105,
      "spokenEnd": 201.19,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "材料少而稳定时，这样做很快；",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.496,
      "audioStart": 201.153,
      "spokenStart": 201.29,
      "spokenEnd": 203.074,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "但智能体还不知道哪一段真正重要，注意力预算已经提前花掉了。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.536,
      "audioStart": 203.03,
      "spokenStart": 203.174,
      "spokenEnd": 206.994,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "按需检索只保留轻量引用，比如文件路径、已保存查询、网页链接、对象标识、目录名和时间戳。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.984,
      "audioStart": 207.006,
      "spokenStart": 207.154,
      "spokenEnd": 213.422,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "上下文里保留地图，到了某个判断确实需要证据时，再打开对应内容。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.752,
      "audioStart": 213.378,
      "spokenStart": 213.522,
      "spokenEnd": 217.552,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这会形成渐进式披露。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.92,
      "audioStart": 217.566,
      "spokenStart": 217.712,
      "spokenEnd": 218.905,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "文件名提示用途，目录结构说明关系，文件大小暗示复杂度，一次搜索结果帮助缩小下一次查询。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.648,
      "audioStart": 218.852,
      "spokenStart": 219.005,
      "spokenEnd": 224.918,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "智能体逐层建立理解，同时只把正在使用的子集放进工作上下文。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.632,
      "audioStart": 224.869,
      "spokenStart": 225.018,
      "spokenEnd": 228.911,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "Claude Code 就体现了这种方法。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.256,
      "audioStart": 228.922,
      "spokenStart": 229.071,
      "spokenEnd": 230.61,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "稳定的项目指令可以预先加载，文件搜索、grep、head 和 tail 负责查看大仓库里的目标片段，不必一次读取所有文件正文。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 7.944,
      "audioStart": 230.557,
      "spokenStart": 230.71,
      "spokenEnd": 237.925,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "取舍同样真实。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.632,
      "audioStart": 237.94,
      "spokenStart": 238.085,
      "spokenEnd": 239.007,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "运行时探索比预加载更慢，导航不佳还会让智能体在错误方向上浪费 token。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.424,
      "audioStart": 238.951,
      "spokenStart": 239.107,
      "spokenEnd": 243.795,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "它需要合适的搜索工具、能说明用途的命名，以及知道什么时候停止探索的规则。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.256,
      "audioStart": 243.745,
      "spokenStart": 243.895,
      "spokenEnd": 248.433,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "因此更实用的是混合策略。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.184,
      "audioStart": 248.448,
      "spokenStart": 248.593,
      "spokenEnd": 250.051,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "预先放入稳定规则、当前目标和几乎每一步都会用到的少量事实；",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.608,
      "audioStart": 250.005,
      "spokenStart": 250.151,
      "spokenEnd": 254.048,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "变化快、细节多或很少使用的材料放到检索入口后面。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.176,
      "audioStart": 254.001,
      "spokenStart": 254.148,
      "spokenEnd": 257.614,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u04",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "边界要根据任务和漏掉信息的代价来定。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3,
      "audioStart": 257.565,
      "spokenStart": 257.714,
      "spokenEnd": 259.981,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "小结。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 259.993,
      "spokenStart": 260.141,
      "spokenEnd": 260.552,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "第一，保留轻量引用，不要预先塞入全部正文。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 260.506,
      "spokenStart": 260.652,
      "spokenEnd": 263.406,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，让 AI 智能体在细节真正相关时再逐步发现。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.104,
      "audioStart": 263.413,
      "spokenStart": 263.566,
      "spokenEnd": 266.938,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，在更聚焦的上下文和额外检索成本之间做取舍。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.104,
      "audioStart": 266.951,
      "spokenStart": 267.098,
      "spokenEnd": 270.481,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "长任务还会带来第二个问题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.304,
      "audioStart": 270.515,
      "spokenStart": 270.661,
      "spokenEnd": 272.235,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "即使上下文一直被认真筛选，智能体执行动作、观察结果、修复错误和累积决定后，窗口仍会填满。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.936,
      "audioStart": 272.194,
      "spokenStart": 272.335,
      "spokenEnd": 278.553,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u03",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "连续工作几小时，可能多次超过可用范围。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.12,
      "audioStart": 278.501,
      "spokenStart": 278.653,
      "spokenEnd": 281.052,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一种方法是压缩。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.752,
      "audioStart": 281.064,
      "spokenStart": 281.212,
      "spokenEnd": 282.243,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "把对话或轨迹总结后开启新窗口，只带上保持连续性所需的决定、未解决问题、约束、证据和下一步动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 7.368,
      "audioStart": 282.188,
      "spokenStart": 282.343,
      "spokenEnd": 288.981,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u03",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "已经完成使命的原始工具输出通常可以退出。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.192,
      "audioStart": 288.928,
      "spokenStart": 289.081,
      "spokenEnd": 291.545,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "压缩存在风险：今天看起来次要的细节，可能后来才显出关键价值。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.944,
      "audioStart": 291.554,
      "spokenStart": 291.705,
      "spokenEnd": 295.94,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "Anthropic 建议先追求高召回，再逐步提高精确度。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.504,
      "audioStart": 295.885,
      "spokenStart": 296.04,
      "spokenEnd": 298.813,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "多带一点内容，通常比丢掉决定性约束更安全。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.312,
      "audioStart": 298.759,
      "spokenStart": 298.913,
      "spokenEnd": 301.481,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二种方法是结构化笔记。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.304,
      "audioStart": 301.493,
      "spokenStart": 301.641,
      "spokenEnd": 303.207,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "智能体把进度、里程碑、发现和开放问题写到窗口之外，需要时再取回相关部分。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.808,
      "audioStart": 303.156,
      "spokenStart": 303.307,
      "spokenEnd": 308.376,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "这样能保留持久工作状态，又不用让整段对话一直在线。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.08,
      "audioStart": 308.326,
      "spokenStart": 308.476,
      "spokenEnd": 311.814,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "专门的 Agent 可以隔离深度探索。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.448,
      "audioStart": 311.819,
      "spokenStart": 311.974,
      "spokenEnd": 313.674,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "主 Agent 保留高层计划，多个专门 Agent 分别研究独立问题，再把压缩后的发现交回。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.616,
      "audioStart": 313.624,
      "spokenStart": 313.774,
      "spokenEnd": 318.666,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "只有并行深挖的价值超过协调成本时，这种方式才值得。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.032,
      "audioStart": 318.611,
      "spokenStart": 318.766,
      "spokenEnd": 322.07,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "选择要看任务形态：持续对话用压缩，有清晰里程碑的迭代工作用笔记，独立而复杂的研究用专门 Agent。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.816,
      "audioStart": 322.087,
      "spokenStart": 322.23,
      "spokenEnd": 328.333,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "无论采用哪种方式，交接都必须保留目标、决定、证据、未知项和下一步动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.544,
      "audioStart": 328.285,
      "spokenStart": 328.433,
      "spokenEnd": 333.262,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "小结。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.128,
      "audioStart": 333.274,
      "spokenStart": 333.422,
      "spokenEnd": 333.833,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "第一，把长轨迹压缩成高召回的连续性摘要。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.192,
      "audioStart": 333.785,
      "spokenStart": 333.933,
      "spokenEnd": 336.407,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，把持久工作状态写进结构化外部笔记。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.36,
      "audioStart": 336.42,
      "spokenStart": 336.567,
      "spokenEnd": 339.208,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，只有聚焦探索值得协调成本时，才使用专门 Agent。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.984,
      "audioStart": 339.217,
      "spokenStart": 339.368,
      "spokenEnd": 342.622,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "把前面的方法整理成一份最小高信号上下文包。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 342.652,
      "spokenStart": 342.802,
      "spokenEnd": 345.558,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它有六部分：结果目标、运行规则、工具地图、典型示例、检索索引和工作状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.928,
      "audioStart": 345.509,
      "spokenStart": 345.658,
      "spokenEnd": 350.863,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p01-u03",
      "sceneId": "c06-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "它足够紧凑，可以人工检查；",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.424,
      "audioStart": 350.811,
      "spokenStart": 350.963,
      "spokenEnd": 352.653,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p01-u04",
      "sceneId": "c06-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "也足够完整，可以支持真实工作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.64,
      "audioStart": 352.603,
      "spokenStart": 352.753,
      "spokenEnd": 354.653,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一部分是结果目标。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.824,
      "audioStart": 354.669,
      "spokenStart": 354.813,
      "spokenEnd": 355.92,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "写清目标、使用者、交付物、验收条件，以及结果要支持的决定。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.704,
      "audioStart": 355.88,
      "spokenStart": 356.02,
      "spokenEnd": 360.004,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p02-u03",
      "sceneId": "c06-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "这样可以避免智能体做出很流畅、很好看，却没有解决真实问题的产物。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.992,
      "audioStart": 359.96,
      "spokenStart": 360.104,
      "spokenEnd": 364.388,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二部分是运行规则。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.92,
      "audioStart": 364.402,
      "spokenStart": 364.548,
      "spokenEnd": 365.741,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "记录硬约束、权限、风险边界、升级节点和停止条件。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.32,
      "audioStart": 365.7,
      "spokenStart": 365.841,
      "spokenEnd": 369.426,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c06-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "把长期规则与临时假设分开，避免一次性的绕行方案悄悄变成永久政策。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.16,
      "audioStart": 369.37,
      "spokenStart": 369.526,
      "spokenEnd": 373.95,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三部分是工具地图和典型示例。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.88,
      "audioStart": 373.969,
      "spokenStart": 374.11,
      "spokenEnd": 376.277,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "每个工具写明使用条件、输入、紧凑输出，以及它不能替代的相邻工具；",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.896,
      "audioStart": 376.229,
      "spokenStart": 376.377,
      "spokenEnd": 380.549,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c06-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "再加入两三个例子，展示主要模式和一条关键边界。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.816,
      "audioStart": 380.509,
      "spokenStart": 380.649,
      "spokenEnd": 383.75,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第四部分是检索索引。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.136,
      "audioStart": 383.761,
      "spokenStart": 383.91,
      "spokenEnd": 385.316,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "给每份来源保存轻量入口、用途标签和打开条件。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.984,
      "audioStart": 385.266,
      "spokenStart": 385.416,
      "spokenEnd": 388.678,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c06-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "智能体不仅要知道证据在哪里，也要知道什么时候必须取回证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.344,
      "audioStart": 388.624,
      "spokenStart": 388.778,
      "spokenEnd": 392.392,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第五部分是工作状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.824,
      "audioStart": 392.405,
      "spokenStart": 392.552,
      "spokenEnd": 393.68,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "记录已完成事项、当前重点、关键决定与证据、未决问题、失败方法和下一步动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.904,
      "audioStart": 393.639,
      "spokenStart": 393.78,
      "spokenEnd": 398.984,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p06-u03",
      "sceneId": "c06-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "到达里程碑就更新状态，再压缩或归档它替代的原始轨迹。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.056,
      "audioStart": 398.93,
      "spokenStart": 399.084,
      "spokenEnd": 402.404,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "小结。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.128,
      "audioStart": 402.416,
      "spokenStart": 402.564,
      "spokenEnd": 402.975,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "第一，用结果目标和运行规则锚定 AI 智能体。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.528,
      "audioStart": 402.926,
      "spokenStart": 403.075,
      "spokenEnd": 405.875,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，用工具地图、典型示例和检索索引指导行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.056,
      "audioStart": 405.887,
      "spokenStart": 406.035,
      "spokenEnd": 409.361,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，用紧凑且持续更新的工作状态保持连续性。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.744,
      "audioStart": 409.373,
      "spokenStart": 409.521,
      "spokenEnd": 412.525,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "AI 智能体忘记重点，不只因为缺信息，也可能因为没有区分的信息太多，共同争夺有限注意力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 6.216,
      "audioStart": 412.551,
      "spokenStart": 412.705,
      "spokenEnd": 418.212,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一，管理完整上下文状态，不只优化提示词。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.6,
      "audioStart": 418.224,
      "spokenStart": 418.372,
      "spokenEnd": 421.254,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c07-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "根据下一步判断需要什么，保留目标、约束、工具、证据和当前状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.16,
      "audioStart": 421.205,
      "spokenStart": 421.354,
      "spokenEnd": 425.795,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，提高信号质量。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.896,
      "audioStart": 425.807,
      "spokenStart": 425.955,
      "spokenEnd": 427.133,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c07-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "用合适层级的指令、最小工具集和少量典型示例，替代脆弱规则与边缘情况堆积。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.928,
      "audioStart": 427.084,
      "spokenStart": 427.233,
      "spokenEnd": 432.443,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，按需检索细节。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.112,
      "audioStart": 432.455,
      "spokenStart": 432.603,
      "spokenEnd": 433.98,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c07-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "稳定且高频的信息放在前面，变化快或专业性强的材料通过明确引用逐步打开。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.76,
      "audioStart": 433.925,
      "spokenStart": 434.08,
      "spokenEnd": 439.114,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最后，用压缩、结构化笔记和六部分最小高信号上下文包保护长任务。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.016,
      "audioStart": 439.129,
      "spokenStart": 439.274,
      "spokenEnd": 443.564,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c07-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "保留信号，按需取细节，持续维护工作状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.456,
      "audioStart": 443.516,
      "spokenStart": 443.664,
      "spokenEnd": 446.392,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "关注 Tiny Agent，成为更擅长使用 AI 的人！",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
